# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md
msgid "Above ground biomass"
msgstr "Biomasse aérienne"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:17
msgid ""
"The biomass of living vegetation, both woody and herbaceous, above the soil "
"including stems, stumps, branches, bark, seeds, and foliage"
msgstr ""
"La biomasse de la végétation vivante, ligneuse et herbacée, au-dessus du "
"sol, y compris les tiges, les souches, les branches, l'écorce, les graines "
"et le feuillage."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
